<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mantra&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="references-small references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> Feuerstein, G. <i>The Deeper Dimension of Yoga</i>. Shambala Publications, Boston, MA. 2003.</li>
<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> Khanna, Madhu (2003). <i>Yantra: The Tantric Symbol of Cosmic Unity.</i> Inner Traditions. ISBN-10: 0892811323 &amp; ISBN-13: 978-0892811328. p.21</li>
